{"tid":2052972,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我諗連登仔話走難應該無諗過香港地理位置問題","createTime":"2020-06-06T02:16:38.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-11T20:06:09.000Z","uid":58841,"like":11,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"54ebaa354949898f6da552ede41e403bd0f467d0","tid":2052972,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:16:38.000Z","msg":"空路:<br />\n而家D機已經CUT撚到每間airline一個禮拜得幾架班次<br />\n連D貨都要排隊排到仆街咁飛出去<br />\n所以走難香港人係一定走唔哂<br />\n陸路:<br />\n要經支那 完<br />\n水路:<br />\n游水去台灣或者越南<br />\n不過到時打仗南海台海一定開緊波<br />\n同埋香港南邊水域大浪到仆街又水深<br />\n分分鐘搭搭下船一個飛彈射鳩落黎你度<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n連登仔以為自己係咁樣走難<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEtedgOU.jpg&amp;h=95c3eb89&amp;s=540\" /><br />\n<br />\n事實上係咁樣走難<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVOid1fD.jpg&amp;h=40e31e71&amp;s=540\" />"},{"pid":"f5cab36f2480fc8a0c7061d3ef3d3962dc6834b7","tid":2052972,"uid":58841,"like":4,"dislike":4,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:18:35.000Z","msg":"所以我俾連登仔既建議係開戰個陣返屋企訓較好過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"514ac1ff40416f909229edf0b417b303dc30b6b6","tid":2052972,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔不願面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走難黎講香港絕對係閪中之閪"},{"pid":"2b370aebfd386578bf73cc606bb2073f74be27c6","tid":2052972,"uid":37796,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"514ac1ff40416f909229edf0b417b303dc30b6b6","tid":2052972,"uid":58841,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:22:53.000Z","msg":"連登仔不願面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n走難黎講香港絕對係閪中之閪"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T02:24:31.000Z","msg":"咁撚多人，冇陸路走路方法就一定係咁"},{"pid":"8ed302cab99d67f9b00a8fd35bc23a33304880f1","tid":2052972,"uid":27605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"sc